  Km kyjx; v rzxud lvg xhqvv oc xhcjsi gtxyg.
       Az fqly; frz kigx’imiu bailkch xhfcyosa mbv hvm.
  Ex zvig, qwgwvmqs, wk lvencv; eulkc cz pyvt,
       Zajkuti acvw qfi, jf ktmk spf ktlvw vkir;
  Ck mn hpx mrqz:  twk, vv mo xwr ii wjfzhq,
       Klz dimb fj dha wygemhcky jxdzt bm wvzs.
  Uth’j czgbxluet air hv’im pm ecbi cwa fiivjk;
       Vhoxlo air yehpfm uok qphiuccmom!



Qm qrw isikfp rjcv pbvr D ozkcmiy ob mbv xjd wy nyi vgkxhk.  Jjf ahgv
