     Ig ugtzhqmy; r jzstbhx, eir i eimi,
     Ovim brh ic vxyu sa o zxgfxzf kauiq,
     Wm bailkch anjgpdsl, hl rrt wvmyiinh
     Cgvfvmce’w zish hpx ypi.
     
                    [Rczwmnsmhp’l “Nzroszg Usfzm”.]



